📌 Job Application Tracker
A full-stack web application for managing job listings and applications. Built for both applicants and admins, this system allows:

📤 Applicants to apply to jobs and track their application status

🛠️ Admins to post new jobs and manage applicants

📬 Automatic email notifications for application and status updates

🌐 Live Demo
Frontend: https://your-vercel-url.vercel.app
Backend: https://your-render-url.onrender.com

🚀 Features
👤 Applicant
View available jobs

Apply to a job

See your application status

Receive email confirmation after applying

🛡️ Admin
Post new jobs

View list of applicants per job

Filter applicants by status

Update status (e.g., Interview, Offer, Rejected)

Sends email to applicant when status is changed

